				<name type="primary" sortindex="1" value="Ice Fox: A Diamond Heist Micro Game" />
			
						                           
						               													<description>Ice Fox is a diamond heist/chase theme 18-card micro game for 2 players. One player takes on the role of the world renowned international diamond thief, Ice Fox, whose mission is to elude capture, steal the diamonds in the museum, and escape through the Exit. The other player takes on the role of the Guard trying to capture the elusive Ice Fox and protect the diamonds, Both characters have unique abilities and gain new abilities as the game goes on. Will the Ice Fox's luck run cold, OR will the Guard be put on ice?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Ice Fox and Guard start on different &amp;quot;tracks&amp;quot; in the museum that only intersect on certain tiles. In each turn, a new tile is added to the map and the player can perform a set number of actions to meet their objective. The Ice Fox can move, turn off lights in a room, and steal a diamond when a diamond room is revealed. The Guard can move, turn on lights in a room, and apprehend. Ice Fox's objective: Get a diamond (or more if you're feeling lucky) and get out. Guard's objective: Capture the Ice Fox!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
